		<p>
			<b>IRC chat on <uri link="http://www.freenode.org/">Freenode</uri>:</b>.
    </p>
    <p>

			The gentoo developers and helpers run the following channels for mutual benefit, it is purely voluntary, and open to everyone.
			Feel free to pop in and say hello! Please keep the language clean in #gentoo and #gentoo-dev. Owners of other Gentoo channels are
			permitted to set their own policies relating to language usage.
    </p>
